text: Giovana Prado Pass (born 30 March 1998) is a Brazilian Olympic dressage rider. Representing Brazil, she competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro where she finished 47th in the individual and 10th in the team competitions. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1998 births Category:Brazilian female equestrians Category:Equestrians at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic equestrians of Brazil
